replies.body:
Lets go over a few things.

All the things you got were champion shards;

Unfortunately randomness comes with this chance, i've opened plenty of the boxes, and i'm still sitting on 15 champion shards (i own all champions, and have 12 in the champion mastery 6+ area on my profile)

And honestly i think it's about 50/50 as to whether you get champion shards or skins.

Chests are harder to get;

If your talking about season start, you have to remember that games are generally worse during school holidays, not only this you are required to get an S- or higher or have a premade partner get an S- or higher, meaning if your not premade and generally struggle yourself with getting S's that it can be rather hard to get them in general (and the system seems to have gotten SLIGHTLY better over time)
